Package: GroupThink
Title: A package for streamlined survey data analysis
Version: 0.0.2.9001
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Samuel Osian", family = "Andrews", email = "soandrews98@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0000-7644-6218"))
Description: GroupThink streamlines traditional survey analysis tasks, such as recoding and presenting Likert-style data and multiple choice data. Its aim is to avoid key bottlenecks in the analysis process, and to prevent common issues and bugs typical of survey analysis code. 
